About Event

​Year-End Wellness Social

​Join us for a FREE luxe wellness social to move, connect, and celebrate the end of 2025 with intention and style.

​📍 Pinstripes – Hillsdale Mall, San Mateo

​📅 December 28, 2025

​⏰ 10:30 AM – 12:30 PM

​

​We’ll start with a 30 minute pop-up yoga class followed by a 30 minute mat Pilates class!

​10:45 am-11:15 am Yoga

​11:15 am-11:45 am Pilates

​Bring your own mat.

​

​After class, enjoy:

​💎 Custom fit permanent jewelry by Link x Lou
